b, and Pronoun respectively, reflecting their grammatical function as independent units.\n\n**PROTOCOL 7: THE FILTER (Size Constraint)**\n- All processed words were longer than a single character, so no entries were discarded based on this protocol.","input_words":["ኦሊቪያና","ኦሊጃንጌ","ኦሊፓ","ኦላናም","ኦላንደር","ኦላንድን","ኦልሳቤት","ኦልቢን","ኦልኮዮ","ኦልፏታል","ኦሖላም","ኦሖላና","ኦመሃጀር","ኦሙ","ኦማዊ","ኦሜትር","ኦሜጋቸውን","ኦሞቲኩ","ኦሪም","ኦሪቶችም","ኦሪየንትድ","ኦሪዬል","ኦሪዮርዳን","ኦሪጂናሎቹ","ኦሪጅናልነትና","ኦራክልና","ኦሬክ","ኦሬጎን","ኦርስቴድ","ኦርሻን"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"daa468e1-6dd8-4987-b352-645529b54bda","created_at":"2026-03-04T08:08:54.509775+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_24/chunk_0608.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገለጥለታለሁ","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ገለጻ","word":"እገላለጽን","synonyms":["expression","description","explanation","statement"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገልጠው","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገልጥ","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገልጥላቸዋለሁ","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገልጥላችሁ","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገልጥላችኋለሁ","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጥ","word":"እገልጥብህ","synonyms":["to reveal","to disclose","to manifest","to explain","to express"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለጽ","word":"እገልጻቸዋለሁ","synonyms":["to express","to explain","to describe","to clarify"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መግለ